race.description: Nosh By Nige Executive Chef Plate (C2)
race.comment: Open contest. CLUBHOUSE (1) is one from one over this distance range and has been thereabouts in recent efforts. Winning rider Mallyon reunites in the saddle and should be going very close to getting the chocolates. MOET AT MIDNIGHT (4) went down by a narrow margin at Grafton last time out and Tomizawa stays in the stirrups. Can make his presence felt with a repeat of that performance. FRIEND IN NEED (6) grows a leg for hoop Thompson who has a win and three placings from just four steers. Include in calculations from the inside marble. WARRIOR BAE (12) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on.
